                         | 
	
                      </span>
                      <span class="meta-date">
                        
		March 20, 2014	
                      </span>
                    </div>
                    <p>
                      MICHAEL W. DOYLE AND JOSEPH E. STIGLITZ
                    </p>
                    <p>
                      Sustainable development cannot be achieved while ignoring extreme disparities. It is imperative that the post-MDG agenda focus on inequality.
                    </p>
                    <p class="readmore">
                      <a title="Permanent Link to Eliminating Extreme Inequality: A Sustainable Development Goal, 2015–2030" rel="nofollow" href="http://www.ethicsandinternationalaffairs.org/2014/eliminating-extreme-inequality-a-sustainable-development-goal-2015-2030/" class="more-link">
