                    <a title="Permanent Link to &lt;i>Special Responsibilities: Global Problems and American Power&lt;/i> by Mlada Bukovansky, Ian Clark, Robyn Eckersley, Richard Price, Christian Reus-Smit, and Nicholas Wheeler" rel="bookmark" href="http://www.ethicsandinternationalaffairs.org/2014/special-responsibilities-global-problems-and-american-power-mlada-bukovansky-ian-clark-robyn-eckersley-richard-price-christian-reus-smit-and-nicholas-wheeler/">
                      <img title="&lt;i>Special Responsibilities: Global Problems and American Power&lt;/i> by Mlada Bukovansky, Ian Clark, Robyn Eckersley, Richard Price, Christian Reus-Smit, and Nicholas Wheeler" alt="&lt;i>Special Responsibilities: Global Problems and American Power&lt;/i> by Mlada Bukovansky, Ian Clark, Robyn Eckersley, Richard Price, Christian Reus-Smit, and Nicholas Wheeler" src="http://www.ethicsandinternationalaffairs.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/9781107021358_p0_v1_s260x420-150x150.jpg" class="thumbnail"/>
